panels.title: FAU DATA CENTER Reading Swarm of Row B and Row A

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.temp as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " Temp 1") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.temp2 as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " Temp 2") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.pdua_power as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " Rack PDU-A Power") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.pdub_power as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " Rack PDU-B Power") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.pdua_ltol_voltage as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " PDU-A Input LtoL Voltage") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  RE.pdub_ltol_voltage as value,
  CONCAT(R.row_id, " ", R.rack_number, " PDU-B Input LtoL Voltage") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
JOIN rack R ON R.rack_id = RE.rack_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
ORDER BY RE.reading_dt, metric ASC

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  SUM(RE.pdub_power) + SUM(RE.pdua_power) as value,
  CONCAT("Rack Power") as metric
FROM rpdu RE
WHERE $__timeFilter(RE.reading_dt)
GROUP BY RE.reading_dt

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(RE.reading_dt) as time_sec,
  SUM(RE.output_power_ltol_phase_1)+SUM(RE.output_power_ltol_phase_2) + SUM(RE.output_power_ltol_phase_3) as value,
  CONCAT("UPS Power") as metric
FROM ups2 RE
WHERE $__timeFilter(reading_dt)
GROUP BY RE.reading_dt
